# Taints & Tolerance
- basically fixes the node to the pod, it is exactly opposite to node affinity

> Taint the node
kubectl taint no rahul-aio-control-plane size=small:NoExecute

> Add this to spec section of pod
tolerations:
- key: "key1"
  operator: "Equal"
  value: "value1"
  effect: "NoSchedule"
